snippet.title: Silent Santicado - Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Silent Santicado is an atmospheric metroidvania set in the ruins of a stone city afflicted with a quiet, unseen curse.


Support on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/vastudios/silent-santicado


Wishlist on Steam: http://steam.pm/app/1287930
